text: not putting more investment in oathbreaker until stats go up. traffic has stabilized though so let's keep it up and going

<@U286Q175Y> you can check out the current stuff at <https://react.edhrec.com>.  registering, logging in/out, forgot password, etc. (all user management stuff) should work.  right now the only 2 features are setting language and regional price source, and I'm working on getting those settings respected everywhere.

the 2 big hurdles remaining are getting it working on non-react pages (I have 2 approaches in mind so I'll just have to dip my toe in each and then pick 1) and beta testing, I figure at some point I'll make <http://react.edhrec.com|react.edhrec.com> open-internet and get some authors to create accounts and see if they run into any bugs or ui confusion
